queries.sql: SELECT c.*,ct.Type FROM `clients` c left join `clienttype` ct on ct.Id= c.Client_Type
SELECT ps.*,pst.Type_Names FROM `quotations` q join `projects` p on p.Quotation_Id = q.Id join `projectscopes` ps on ps.Project_Id = p.Id join `projectscopetypes` pst on ps.ProjectScopeType = pst.Id

SELECT q.Client_Id,c.Name,a.*,p.Id,p.Project_Name,p.Delivery_Date,p.Quotation_Id,p.Lump_Sump_Charges,p.Project_file,p.project_file_link,p.notes,p.project_type,p.deliver_file,p.status as projectStatus FROM `quotations` q JOIN projects p on p.Quotation_Id = q.Id JOIN clients c on c.Id = q.Client_Id LEFT JOIN assignproject a on a.project_id = p.Id GROUP by p.Id order by p.Id desc

SELECT user_id, project_id, AVG(max_progress) AS avg_max_progress FROM (SELECT user_id, project_id, MAX(progress) AS max_progress FROM projectprogress GROUP BY user_id, project_id ) AS max_progress_table GROUP BY user_id, project_id;
SELECT a.*,u.username,u.profile_image FROM `assignproject` a join users u on u.id = a.user_id JOIN projects p on p.Id = a.project_id

SELECT q.*,c.Name as Client_Name, c.Email_Address as Client_EmailAddress FROM `quotations` q join `clients` c on q.Client_Id = c.Id JOIN projects p on p.Quotation_Id= q.Id WHERE p.Lump_Sump_Charges =0 GROUP by q.Id ORDER BY q.Id DESC
